settings -> The error you're encountering is related to Django's APPEND_SLASH setting. When APPEND_SLASH is set to True (which is the default), Django appends a trailing slash to URLs that don't end with one. This can cause an issue with POST requests because Django doesn't redirect POST requests.

APPEND_SLASH = False